import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { useAuth } from '../contexts/AuthContext'; const Dashboard = () => { const { user } = useAuth(); const quickActions = [ { title: 'Make Contribution', description: 'Contribute to Chama Smart', link: '/contributions/pay', icon: '💰', color: 'success' }, { title: 'Apply for Loan', description: 'Request a loan from Chama Smart', link: '/loans/apply', icon: '🏦', color: 'info' }, { title: 'Schedule Meeting', description: 'Schedule a Chama Smart meeting', link: '/meetings/create', icon: '📅', color: 'warning' }, { title: 'View Reports', description: 'Check Chama Smart financial reports', link: '/reports', icon: '📊', color: 'primary' } ]; const stats = [ { label: 'Your Contributions', value: 'KSh 0', color: 'success' }, { label: 'Active Loans', value: '0', color: 'info' }, { label: 'Upcoming Meetings', value: '0', color: 'warning' }, { label: 'Member Since', value: 'Jan 2024', color: 'primary' } ]; return (

Chama Smart Dashboard

Welcome back, {user?.first_name}! Here's your Chama Smart overview.

{/* Stats Cards */}
{stats.map((stat, index) => (
{stat.value}

{stat.label}

))}
{/* Quick Actions */}

Quick Actions

{quickActions.map((action, index) => (
{action.icon}
{action.title}

{action.description}

))}
{/* Recent Activity */}
Recent Activity

No recent activity to display.

Make a contribution or participate in Chama Smart activities to see your activity here.

); }; export default Dashboard;
